          <div xml:id="dictFrontPage_Baghdad" n="BAGHDAD DICTIONARY">
            <head>A Machine-readable Dictionary of Baghdad Arabic</head>
            
            <p>Compiled by <hi rend="italic">Stephan Procházka</hi> 
                and <hi rend="italic">Fady Yousuf</hi></p>
              
            <p>The current version contains ~1100 entries and examples.</p>
            <p>To query the dictionary click <ref target="func:openDict_Baghdad()">here</ref>.</p>
            <p>For details as to how to formulate meaningful dictionary queries consult 
                the <rs ref="text:dictFrontPage_Tunis"> examples of the TUNICO dictionary</rs>.</p>
              
            <p xml:space="preserve">We also host the <ref target="text:vicavLearning_tb_baghdad/ABC">audio files</ref> of the
            Lehrbuch des Irakisch-Arabischen by Bettina Leitner, Fady German,
            Stephan Procházka. Harrassowitz 2021.</p>
